                  </choice> not flesh from the Virgin Mary.<lb/>
This Error is flat against the first promise of Christ, Gen.<lb/>
3. The seed of the woman shall <normalised orig="breake" auto="true">break</normalised> the serpents head. Against<lb/>
the promise made to Abraham, Gen. 22. In thy seed, &amp;c. To<lb/>
David, <normalised orig="Psal" auto="true">Psalm</normalised>. 132.11. <quote type="psalm" ana="Ps 132.11">Of the fruit of thy body</quote>, &amp;c. <normalised orig="Luk" auto="true">Luck</normalised>. 1.<lb/>
