                  <lb/>
St. Peter saith, Acts 2.39. <quote type="biblical" ana="Acts 2.39">The promise is made to you and<lb/>
                     <pb n="4"/>
                     <lb/>
your children;</quote> and therefore be <normalised orig="baptized" auto="true">baptised</normalised>. To whom the promise<lb/>
