<normalised orig="Againe" auto="true">Again</normalised>, the faith of the Parents may warrant their Infants<lb/>
<normalised orig="baptisme" auto="true">baptism</normalised>: yea, though they have but an <normalised orig="historicall" auto="true">historical</normalised> faith and not<lb/>
