Moreover these phrases, teach and <normalised orig="baptize" auto="true">baptise</normalised>, repent and <normalised orig="beleeve" auto="true">believe</normalised>,<lb/>
<normalised orig="beleeve" auto="true">believe</normalised> &amp; be <normalised orig="baptized" auto="true">baptised</normalised>, are meant of such as were of riper years,<lb/>
and made profession of the Christian faith, or else the estate of<lb/>
