<normalised orig="affirme" auto="true">affirm</normalised> is an horrible indignity offered unto Christ.<lb/>
Last of all most blasphemously they call <normalised orig="baptisme" auto="true">baptism</normalised> of Christian<lb/>
<normalised orig="mens" auto="true">men's</normalised> children the <normalised orig="marke" auto="true">mark</normalised> of the beast, and to come from Antichrist,<lb/>
and especially from Pope Innocent the third, who lived<lb/>
