And <normalised orig="Origen" auto="true">Origin</normalised>, who lived about the <normalised orig="yeare" auto="true">year</normalised> 226. about 1000.<lb/>
<normalised orig="yeares" auto="true">years</normalised> before Pope Innocent, whom the Anabaptists would<lb/>
make the author of pedobaptisme.<lb/>
The Russians who received the faith from St. Andrew the<lb/>
Apostle, and account the Pope of Rome an <normalised orig="Heretick" auto="true">Heretic</normalised>, hold a necessity<lb/>
of <normalised orig="baptisme" auto="true">baptism</normalised>, and put to death them that neglect and deride<lb/>
<normalised orig="baptisme" auto="true">baptism</normalised>: what would they <normalised orig="doe" auto="true">do</normalised> with these men who<lb/>
